<div class="row">
  
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 section-heading">
      <h1>What&rsquo;s New</h1>
      
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
      <ul>
<li><span style="color:red"> <b>[Paper]: </b> </span> A <span style="color:red"> <b>Survey on Community Detection </b></span>was released (<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2101.01669.pdf" target="_blank">Click Here</a> )(06/01/2021).</li>
<li><span style="color:red"> <b>[Paper]: </b> </span> One paper on <a href="../../publication/aaai-2021-wan/">Contrastive Graph Learning</a> was accepted by AAAI-21  (02/12/2020).</li>
<li><span style="color:orange"> [Award]: </span> The Best Student Paper Award at <a href="http://icdm2020.bigke.org/" target="_blank">ICDM-2020</a>  for <a href="../../publication/icdm-20-wu/">Open-World Graph Learning</a> (13/11/20).</li>
<li><span style="color:blue"> <b>[CFP]:</b></span> Special Issue on <a href="https://cis.ieee.org/images/files/Documents/call-for-papers/tnnls/CFP_SS_DNNGTMAA.pdf" target="_blank">Graph Neural Networks</a> in <a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/RecentIssue.jsp?punumber=5962385" target="_blank">IEEE TNNLS</a>  (<span style="color:red"><b>Top Journal, CORE A*, IF: 8.793</b></span>).</li>
<li><span style="color:red"> <b>[Paper]: </b> </span> One paper on <a href="../../publication/tmc-20-wang/">Task Graph Oriented Mobile Crowdsourcing</a>  was accepted by <a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/RecentIssue.jsp?punumber=7755" target="_blank">IEEE Trans. Mobile Computing</a> as a Regular Paper (CORE A*, IF:5.112)(13/11/2020)</li>
<li><span style="color:blue"> <b>[Summary]: </b> </span> How popular is GNN? Check out a summary of NeurIPS-20 papers on Graph Machine Learning <a href="../../post/NIPS_2020_GML.pdf">[Link]</a>.</li>
<li><span style="color:red"> <b>[Paper]: </b> </span> One paper on <a href="../../publication/tpami-20-zhang/">Neural Architecture Search</a> was accepted by <a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/RecentIssue.jsp?punumber=34" target="_blank">IEEE TPAMI</a> as a Regular Paper (CORE A*, IF: 17.86)(27/10/2020)<span style="color:red"> (Top Journal in AI)  </span></li>
<li><span style="color:red"> <b>[Paper]: </b> </span> Three papers were accepted by <a href="https://neurips.cc/" target="_blank">NeurIPS-2020</a> as full papers (CORE A*, Acceptance Rate: 20%)(26/09/2020)<span style="color:red"> (Top Conference in Machine Learning)  </span>

