<li><span style="color:red"> <b>[Paper]: </b> </span>  One Paper on <a href="../../publication/tcyb-2019-wang/">Influence Analysis on Geo-Social Networks</a> is Accepted by <a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/RecentIssue.jsp?punumber=6221036" target="_blank">IEEE Trans. on Cybernetics</a> (IF: 8.803) (13/03/2019).</li>
<li><span style="color:red"> <b>[Paper]: </b> </span>  One Paper on <a href="../../publication/wang-time-2019/">Time Series Feature Learning</a> is Accepted by Pattern Recognition (18/12/2018).</li>
